{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":113186,"duration_api_ms":112149,"num_turns":13,"result":"Done. Changes made:\n\n**Controller** — removed `Mono.deferContextual`, `subscribeOn`, `onErrorResume`, `doFinally`, and the `nettyOffloadExecutor` dependency. The method now:\n1. Prepares the request\n2. Registers the callback future\n3. Publishes to Redis\n4. Calls `future.get(timeout, SECONDS)` to block until the consumer completes it\n5. Returns `ResultDTO<?>` directly, with try-catch for timeout/error handling\n\n**Test** — removed the `TestConfig` that provided the `nettyOffloadExecutor` bean and the timeout test (which relied on Mono scheduling behavior). The remaining tests work unchanged since WebFlux supports blocking return types.\n\n**Note**: `NettyOffLoadThreadPoolConfig` is now unused by this controller. If nothing else references it, you may want to remove it.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"7817aa69-6b3f-4b40-95f1-8f6f041af9c9","total_cost_usd":0.541413,"usage":{"input_tokens":14,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30822,"cache_read_input_tokens":375411,"output_tokens":6440,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30822,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":14,"outputTokens":6440,"cacheReadInputTokens":375411,"cacheCreationInputTokens":30822,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.541413,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"8945a617-5286-4668-9421-325cab2aa19c"}
